+++tuck+me+in+for+the+night.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++Often%2C+the+monsters+would+wake+me+up+in+the+middle+of+the+night%2C+and+I+would+go+crying+into+my+parents%27+bedroom.%0D%0A++++Mother+would+say%2C+%22Lou%2C+go+lie+down+with+Susan+in+her+room%2C%22+and+he+would+wake+up%2C+without+complaint%2C+and+stay+with%0D%0A++++me+until+the+monsters+left%2C+and+I+fell+fast+asleep.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3D783face5-379b-4d02-b10d-715da5269473.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3ECensus+of+the+jewish+orphanage+where+Louis+was+an+%22inmate%22+at+1+year+old.%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3E1920+Census+record+of+Louis+%28Lewis%29+Goodman+at+the+Cleveland+Hebrew+Orphans+Home.%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3D16035c4d-d681-4274-a155-19ddecf5189c.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3ELouis+H+Goodman+as+a+young+man%2C+maybe+5+or+6+years+old%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++Later%2C+he+would+do+the+same+with+my+%3Ca+href%3D%22person%3Fid%3Dc2b45e41-a46f-4cbf-965d-4f4fcf01d610%22%3EByron%3C%2Fa%3E+and+%3Ca%0D%0A++++++++href%3D%22person%3Fid%3Debb6f61d-20eb-421f-967a-71e0bfd7cf9b%22%3EElysa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C+but+he+embellished+it+a+little+for+them.+He%0D%0A++++would+count+their+toes%2C+constantly+making+mistakes%2C+so+that+he+would+have+to+count+them+again+and+again.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++Usually+on+warm-weather+Sundays+when+I+was+a+child%2C+we+looked+forward+to+his+delicious+barbeque.+He+would+start+the%0D%0A++++charcoal+in+the+brick+barbeque+pit+which+was+some+distance+from+the+house.+I+was+in+charge+of+holding+the+bowl+of%0D%0A++++barbeque+sauce+%28he+only+used+Maul%27s+with+Tabasco+and+Worcestershire+thrown+in%2C+for+good+measure%29%2C+and+every+now+and%0D%0A++++then+he+would+teach+me+the+finer+points+of+basting+the+kosher+veal+ribs+or+chicken.+%22It%27s+time+to+turn+them%2C+Susan.%0D%0A++++Give+them+a+good+basting+with+the+brush.+Now%2C+turn+%27em+again.%22+Finally%2C+the+meat+would+be+just+perfect%2C+crispy%2C+and%0D%0A++++glistening+with+the+many+layers+of+sauce%2C+and+he+would+take+his+knife+and+cut+off+a+small+piece+from+the+best+part%2C%0D%0A++++cut+that+into+two+pieces%2C+and+each+one+of+us+would+eat+a+%22sample%22.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3D45676896-4ba6-41f4-80d7-ee85b6ef71fb.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3ESarah+Goodman%2C+Bertha+Goodman%2C+and+Louis%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3EA+picture+of+Sarah+Goodman%2C+Bertha+%28Blema%29+Goodman%2C+and+Louis+Goodman+in+the+1920s%2C+sitting+on+a+porch%0D%0A++++++++++++swing.%0D%0A++++++++%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3De8a1ba81-0e94-4f21-86c4-1761a1b196fe.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3ELouis+Goodman%27s+1936+yearbook+photo+from+Lorain+Ohio%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++On+these+days%2C+he+would+also+hand+cut+French+fries+from+huge+Idaho+potatoes.+He+would+stand+at+the+counter+in+the%0D%0A++++kitchen%2C+and+patiently+peel%2C+slice%2C+turn%2C+and+slice+the+potatoes+again+so+that+the+French+fries+would+be+wonderful%0D%0A++++for+us.+And+they+always+were.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++On+Henry+Street%2C+my+brother+and+I+would+often+play+in+the+%22dollhouse%22+which+Daddy+built.+I+remember+him+hammering%0D%0A++++and+nailing+the+boards+together.+It+was+situated+in+an+area+of+the+yard+that+was+somewhat+near+the+big+climbing%0D%0A++++tree.+I+loved+that+dollhouse%3B+it+always+seemed+so+mysterious+and+protective.+It+was+a+real+house%2C+with+a+roof+and%0D%0A++++windows%2C+nothing+prefabricated.+We+placed+chairs+and+bookcases+in+there+so+we+could+read.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3Da50679aa-ccc1-49f0-a01d-a47b07ee8874.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3Ecloseup+of+Louis+Goodman+in+yearbook%2C+1935%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3D8b49df17-b1ac-4171-b10f-4ae6a8510f1d.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3ELouis+Goodman%27s+High+School+Diploma%2C+1937%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3EFrom+the+Lorain+High+School%2C+1937%2C+Lorain+Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++Daddy+would+throw+a+baseball+back+and+forth+with+Gary+every+night+after+he+came+home+from+work.+If+he+ever%0D%0A++++complained+about+it%2C+I+was+never+aware.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++Fishing+was+Daddy%27s+passion.+He+built+a+small%2C+rustic+cabin+at+Snow+Lake%2C+in+Mississippi%2C+where+we+went+most%0D%0A++++weekends+from+the+time+I+was+in+second+grade.+I+remember+when+he+first+showed+us+the+property.+For+each+lot%0D%0A++++purchased%2C+the+developers+were+offering+a+discount+of+two+hundred+dollars+or+a+Shetland+pony.+I+couldn%27t+wait+to%0D%0A++++ride+and+play+with+the+Pony%21+To+this+day%2C+I%27ve+never+seen+one+of+these+animals+up+close.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A+%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3D05e91c38-d194-4a34-ad5f-78e0fb02423f.jpg%22+alt%3D%22%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELorain+Ohio%2C+1935%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++Because+my+parents+were+Orthodox%2C+my+father+couldn%27t+use+the+fishing+boat+on+Shabbos%2C+and+so%2C+on+that+day%2C+we+would%0D%0A++++walk+the+mile+to+the+man-made+lake%27s+sandy+beach+to+go+swimming%2C+or+we+would+read.+But+on+Sunday%2C+we+would+all+climb%0D%0A++++into+the+boat+and+go+%22trolling%22%2C+and+catch+delicious+bass+and+brim.+He+would+take+us+to+the+quiet%2C+shady+coves+in%0D%0A++++the+lake+where+the+brim+were%2C+and+we+would+wait+patiently%2C+without+talking%2C+so+they+wouldn%27t+know+that+we+were%0D%0A++++looking+for+them.+Even+though+he+usually+used+professionally-made+lures%2C+he+would+often+stop+on+the+way+to+Snow+Lake%0D%0A++++to+buy+crickets+or+minnows.+I+still+remember+sitting+on+the+pier+with+him+while+he+gave+me+tips+on+how+to+hook+a%0D%0A++++minnow.+I+don%27t+think+I+would+ever+touch+the+crickets.+When+the+fish+were+caught%2C+we+would+putter+back+to+our+pier%2C%0D%0A++++and+he+would+bring+the+line+of+fish+into+the+house+and+throw+the+fish+into+the+sink.+Eventually%2C+he+scaled+and%0D%0A++++cleaned+these+delicacies%2C+and+my+mother+would+fry+them.+He+always+loved+fried+fish.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3Df1a95422-5ca9-3b00-a6b2-ea1dda3fc66f.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3EGrandma+Margie+Goodman%2C+Grampa+Louis+Goodman%2C+Susan+Katz+and+Ron+Katz+at+Byron+and+Susanne%27s+wedding+in%0D%0A++++++++++++Braselton%2C+Georgia%2C+Chateau+Elan%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++For+a+few+years%2C+I+had+the+chance+to+work+with+him.+I+gained+an+appreciation+of+the+difficulties+he+and+my+mother%0D%0A++++had+in+persevering+with+their+business.+But+he+always+maintained+a+sweet+and+caring+disposition%2C+even+when+I+really%0D%0A++++screwed+up.+He+would+listen+as+I+talked+to+customers%2C+and+ever+so+often+he+would+give+me+advice+in+such+a+sweet+way%0D%0A++++that+I+didn%27t+realize+until+much+later+that+I+had+so+much+to+learn.+%22Less+said%2C+best+said%2C%22+took+on+an+important%0D%0A++++meaning+to+me.+Also%2C+%22If+you+only+say+the+truth%2C+you+won%27t+have+to+remember+what+you+said.%22+Daddy+was+a+brilliant%0D%0A++++man