.%29%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3Dd4cc0073-efc8-4118-a38c-c8405f50ce21.jpg%22+alt%3D%22Louis+Goodman%26apos%3Bs+Model+A+car%22%3E%0D%0A%3Cp%3E+Once%2C+when+yet+another+irritated+driver+who+was+behind%0D%0A++++him+on+the+road+started+honking+his+horn%2C+my+father+calmly+stated%2C+%22If+he+wanted+to+get+there+earlier%2C+he+should%0D%0A++++have+left+earlier.%22+He+never+acknowledged+that%2C+just+possibly%2C+it+was+that+he+was+driving+too+slowly.+A+number+of%0D%0A++++years+ago%2C+I+was+driving+somewhere+from+my+home%2C+late+as+usual%2C+and+kind+of+speeding.+I+turned+right+onto+the+main%0D%0A++++road+and+saw+a+major+traffic+jam.+Obviously%2C+there+had+been+a+bad+accident.+In+one+lane%2C+cars+were+lined+up+as+far%0D%0A++++as+the+eye+could+see%2C+and+I+knew+that+I+would+never+get+wherever+it+was+that+I+was+going.+Finally%2C+I+was+able+to%0D%0A++++pull+over+to+the+left+lane+and+speed+up+around+the+line+of+cars.+At+the+head+of+the+line+was+my+father.%0D%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3Deb65c337-79f2-40fb-a854-7acb90ccbd73.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3ELouis+and+Margie+on+a+vacation%2C+1944%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cfigure%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cimg+loading%3D%22lazy%22+alt%3D%22%22+src%3D%22photo%3Fname%3Df8dd6a9f-756a-4e0e-92fa-df2be952ddb4.jpg%22%3E%0D%0A++++%3Cfigcaption%3E%0D%0A++++++++%3Cp%3EAlex+Milaski%2C+Sarah+Kapelow%2C+Louis+Goodman%2C+Saul+Kapelow+in+the+late+1940s.%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A++++%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%0D%0A%3C%2Ffigure%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3E%0D%0A++++In+later+years%2C+my+parents+did+well+financially%2C+and+when+my+brother+and+I+were+in+college%2C+the+family+was+able+to%0D%0A++++travel.+I+remember+one+trip+that+we+took+to+Europe+when+we+visited+a+number+of+countries.+My+favorite+was+France.+I%0D%0A++++had+always+loved+the+sound+of+the+French+language%2C+and+I+was+taking+a+number+of+co